## ‚ö° Quick Troubleshooting

### App Won't Open
1. Force quit and reopen
2. Restart your device
3. Check for iOS updates
4. Reinstall the app
5. Contact support if persists

### Audio Not Playing
1. Check device volume
2. Check mute switch
3. Close other audio apps
4. Try different lullaby
5. Restart app
6. Check audio file integrity

### AI Story Generation Fails
1. Check internet connection
2. Try simpler theme
3. Wait 30 seconds and retry
4. Check if API service is down
5. Contact support if continues

### Voice Commands Not Working
1. Grant microphone permission (Settings ‚Üí DreamWeave)
2. Speak clearly and slowly
3. Check for background noise
4. Try again in quiet environment
5. Restart app

### HealthKit Not Connecting
1. Grant HealthKit permission (Settings ‚Üí Privacy ‚Üí Health)
2. Open Apple Health app
3. Check DreamWeave has read access
4. Restart both apps
5. Re-authorize in DreamWeave settings

### Smart Lights Not Syncing
1. Ensure lights are HomeKit compatible
2. Check Home app shows lights
3. Grant HomeKit permission
4. Lights must be on same WiFi
5. Restart Home app and DreamWeave

