## üí≥ Billing & Subscriptions

### During Beta (Current)
- All features FREE
- No billing
- No payment info required
- Full access for testing

### After Beta Launch

**Subscription Questions:**
- Managed through Apple App Store
- View subscriptions: iOS Settings ‚Üí [Your Name] ‚Üí Subscriptions
- Cancel: Same location, tap DreamWeave ‚Üí Cancel
- Billing: Handled by Apple

**Refund Requests:**
- Contact Apple Support directly
- We cannot process refunds
- Apple's refund policy applies
- Request within 90 days of purchase

**Billing Issues:**
- Check Apple payment method
- Verify App Store account
- Contact Apple Support
- We can verify subscription status

